BT 1 0 0 1 0 62.8 Tm .376815 Tw 14.5 TL /F1 9.7 Tf .109804 .141176 .2 rg (Everything a pharmacist needs to know about how a drug behaves - whether it ionises, dissolves in water or) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.22348 Tw (fat, reacts, or binds a receptor - ultimately traces back to how electrons are arranged around atoms. That) Tj T* 0 Tw 3.302659 Tw (arrangement, called the ) Tj /F2 9.7 Tf (electronic structure) Tj /F1 9.7 Tf (, is governed not by classical physics but by ) Tj /F2 9.7 Tf (quantum) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.447547 Tw (mechanics) Tj /F1 9.7 Tf (, the framework that describes matter at the scale of individual particles. This opening section) Tj T* 0 Tw (builds the conceptual foundation on which every later topic rests.) Tj T* ET
