BT 1 0 0 1 0 85 Tm .156382 Tw 16 TL /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg (A pharmacist is, at heart, a custodian of therapeutic substances. Beyond supplying medicines, the pharmacist) Tj T* 0 Tw .867031 Tw (carries responsibility for guaranteeing that every product they manufacture, compound, dispense, distribute) Tj T* 0 Tw .476492 Tw (or sell is fit for its purpose. "Fit" here is a multi-dimensional judgement: the medicine must be correct in its) Tj T* 0 Tw .878556 Tw /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (chemical identity) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg (, ) Tj /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (purity) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg (, ) Tj /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (potency) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg (, ) Tj /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (stability) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg (, ) Tj /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (efficacy) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg ( and ) Tj /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (safety) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg (, and it must be acceptable to the patient) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.600844 Tw (who ultimately takes it. Quality is therefore not a single test but a verdict assembled from many quality) Tj T* 0 Tw (characteristics.) Tj T* ET
