.109804 .141176 .203922 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 80.9 Tm /F4 10.3 Tf 15.2 TL .935497 Tw (The way the profession defines and defends quality has shifted dramatically over time. In earlier practice, quality) Tj T* 0 Tw .544809 Tw (was judged by a handful of checks on the finished article \227 appearance, colour, odour, identity, hardness, average) Tj T* 0 Tw .192903 Tw (weight and similar surface properties. Modern pharmaceutical practice treats those checks as necessary but nowhere) Tj T* 0 Tw 4.607704 Tw (near sufficient. Today quality is engineered into the entire manufacturing chain through comprehensive) Tj T* 0 Tw .863963 Tw (quality-assurance systems that begin at raw-material sourcing and end only when the finished product reaches the) Tj T* 0 Tw (patient.) Tj T* ET
