BT 1 0 0 1 0 20.1 Tm /F4 10.3 Tf 15.2 TL 2.23661 Tw (Three related but distinct ideas structure modern pharmaceutical quality. It helps to hold them apart, because) Tj T* 0 Tw (examiners frequently ask you to distinguish them.) Tj T* ET
