BT 1 0 0 1 0 35.3 Tm 15.2 TL /F5 10.3 Tf .109804 .141176 .203922 rg (Good Manufacturing Practice \(GMP\)) Tj /F4 10.3 Tf ( is the set of regulations and guidelines ensuring that drugs are consistently) Tj T* (produced and controlled to quality standards. Where QC tests the output, GMP governs the process itself \227 facility) Tj T* (design, equipment, personnel training, documentation and process validation \227 and it is essentially ) Tj /F5 10.3 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (proactive) Tj /F4 10.3 Tf .109804 .141176 .203922 rg (,) Tj T* ET
