BT 1 0 0 1 0 69 Tm 1.265023 Tw 16 TL /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg (An ) Tj /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (immunoassay) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg ( is a bioanalytical method that uses antibodies as reagents to detect or quantify specific) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.141031 Tw (analytes through antigen\226antibody complex formation. Its power lies in exquisite ) Tj /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (specificity) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg ( \(biological) Tj T* 0 Tw .042556 Tw (recognition\) married to high ) Tj /F5 11 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (sensitivity) Tj /F4 11 Tf .058824 .105882 .207843 rg ( \227 often reaching picogram-per-millilitre levels \227 which is why it is) Tj T* 0 Tw .998293 Tw (indispensable in therapeutic drug monitoring, pharmacokinetics, biopharmaceutical QC, anti-drug-antibody) Tj T* 0 Tw (detection and clinical diagnostics.) Tj T* ET
