BT 1 0 0 1 0 65.7 Tm 1.027697 Tw 15.2 TL /F4 10.3 Tf .109804 .141176 .203922 rg (Because the binding event itself is invisible, a ) Tj /F5 10.3 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (label) Tj /F4 10.3 Tf .109804 .141176 .203922 rg ( converts it into a measurable signal. Common labels include) Tj T* 0 Tw -0.008073 Tw (enzymes \(HRP, alkaline phosphatase\), radioisotopes \() Tj /F4 8.3 Tf 5.15 Ts (125) Tj /F4 10.3 Tf 0 Ts (I, ) Tj /F4 8.3 Tf 5.15 Ts (3) Tj /F4 10.3 Tf 0 Ts (H, ) Tj /F4 8.3 Tf 5.15 Ts (14) Tj /F4 10.3 Tf 0 Ts (C\), fluorescent dyes \(FITC, Alexa Fluor, Cy3/Cy5\),) Tj T* 0 Tw 4.372068 Tw (chemiluminescent compounds \(acridinium esters\), and colloidal particles \(gold, latex\). Signal intensity is) Tj T* 0 Tw 3.079012 Tw (interpolated against a ) Tj /F5 10.3 Tf .709804 .070588 0 rg (dose\226response \(calibration\) curve) Tj /F4 10.3 Tf .109804 .141176 .203922 rg ( \227 typically sigmoidal, fitted with 4-parameter or) Tj T* 0 Tw (5-parameter logistic models \227 to yield concentration.) Tj T* ET
